The 4 United States Geological Survey (USGS) 1:24,000 scale topographic maps used to determine the boundary of the Goose Gap viticultural area are titled: 

(1) Benton City, WA, 2017; 

(2) Richland, WA, 2017; 

(3) Badger Mountain, WA, 2017; and 

(4) Webber Canyon, WA, 2017.
